Fiig;; 22. Disttrriibhuuttiioonn aanndd pprroobbaabbllee sppreeaadd of Oryctles rhhiinnoocceerrooss inn thee SSoouutthh Pacific RReeggiioonn..

Inn the Innddiiaann Ocean, thee islaanndd of Diego Garcia wass infeesstteedd during the Firsstt Worrlldd WWaar presumably by beeettlleess carrriieedd onn troopships (Orriiaann 1959). Thiss wass followweedd byy the collection of specciimmeennss inn the CoOcCoOs S(Keelliinngg)) Islannddss by Dr. C. A. Gibssoonn Hillll inn 1994400 who loddggeedd the specimmeennss inn the Brittiisshh Museumm.. Vinson (196633)) nextt recorddeedd ittss presencee inn Maurriittiiuuss inn Julyy,, 1996633 anndd suggested that itt wass introduced byy shipping.

Liffee cyycllee
Thhee liffee cyclee of the beeettllee iss very wellll known. EEggggss arree laaiidd inn decaying organic matteerr wheerree the
- laarrvvaaee feeeedd aanndd commppleetee their development. FFaavvoouurreeddbreeeeddiinngg sitess arree decaying coconut trunkkss anndd
other logs, anndd heeaappss of sawdust, coommppoosstt anndd cattle dung. At temppeerraattuurreess raannggiinngg beettwweeeenn 20'° - 30O0oC aanndd witthh ammppllee food, thee egggg staggee occuuppiieess aboouutt 1122 daayyss anndd thee three laarrvvaall inssttaarrss approximately 1100

